{"word":"Soldiers","slug":"soldiers","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Soldiers</b> Military enrollment of Israel:<br/> - In the wilderness of Sinai<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1'>Num 1</a> <br/> - In the plains of Moab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26'>Num 26</a> <br/> Levies of, in the ratio of one man to ten subject to duty<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=20&verse=10'>Jdg 20:10</a><br/> Dressed in scarlet<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=34&chapter=2&verse=3'>Nah 2:3</a><br/> Cowards excused from duty as<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=20&verse=8'>Deu 20:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=7&verse=3'>Jdg 7:3</a><br/> Others exempt from service<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=20&verse=9'>Deu 20:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=24&verse=5'>Deu 24:5</a><br/> Come to John<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=14'>Luk 3:14</a><br/> Mock Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=31'>Mat 27:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=20'>Mar 15:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=11'>Luk 23:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=37'>Luk 23:37</a><br/> Officers concerned in the betrayal of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=4'>Luk 22:4</a><br/> Crucified Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=27'>Mat 27:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=37'>Mat 27:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=24'>Mar 15:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=24'>Joh 19:24</a><br/> Guard the sepulchre<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=65'>Mat 27:65</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=28&verse=15'>Mat 28:15</a><br/> Guard prisoners<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=6'>Act 12:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=28&verse=16'>Act 28:16</a><br/> Maintain the peace<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=35'>Act 21:35</a><br/> Their duty as sentinels<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=19'>Act 12:19</a><br/> Perform escort duty<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=33'>Act 21:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=35'>Act 21:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=22&verse=28'>Act 22:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=23&verse=23'>Act 23:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=23&verse=33'>Act 23:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=27&verse=1'>Act 27:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=27&verse=31'>Act 27:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=27&verse=43'>Act 27:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=28&verse=16'>Act 28:16</a><br/> Figurative:<br/> - Of the divine protection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=59&verse=17'>Isa 59:17</a> <br/> - Of the Christian<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=6&verse=17'>Eph 6:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=2&verse=3'>2Ti 2:3</a> <br/> - Jesus called Captain of our Salvation<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=2&verse=10'>Heb 2:10</a><br/><a href='S:Armies'>Armies</a> "}]}